description: Try our easy to follow Caramelised Onion Tart recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Caramelised Onion Tart Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 200°C. Join 2 sheets frozen puff pastry together then trim to a 20x32cm rectangle. Mark a 2cmwide border around edge and prick centre with a fork. Bake for 15 minutes. Spread with onion and top with crumbled feta and thyme sprigs. Bake for 15 minutes or until golden.
